&lt;p id="SeruAu"&gt;What are the “favorites” articles? Well, every month or so, we like to ask our staff &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/22344288/favorite-gadgets-tech-lgear-aptops-headphones-kitchen-recommendations"&gt;about their favorite stuff&lt;/a&gt; — whether it’s board games, smart tech, or kitchen gadgets. And the results are usually quirky, personal, and a lot of fun.&lt;/p&gt;
