&lt;div class="iframely-embed"&gt;&lt;div class="iframely-responsive" style="padding-bottom: 100%;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.threads.net/@mosseri/post/DA55gP6xqMb" data-iframely-url="https://cdn.iframe.ly/api/iframe?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40mosseri%2Fpost%2FDA55gP6xqMb&amp;amp;key=9ef4a209439e42bc59783ba959d50197"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p id="XUK76q"&gt;Others, like Jorge...&lt;/p&gt;
